
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "AboutUs";
}

<div class="about-us-container">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p>Welcome to Your Pet Shop Name! We are passionate about pets and committed to providing the best care, products, and services for your furry, feathered, and scaly friends. Our team of experienced pet lovers is here to help you with all your pet needs, whether it's finding the right food, toys, or accessories, or providing expert advice on pet care.</p>
    <p>Our mission is to create a community of pet lovers who share the same love and respect for animals as we do. We believe that pets are family, and we are dedicated to ensuring that your pets live happy, healthy lives.</p>

    <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
    <div class="row team">
        <div class="col-md-4 team-member">
            <img src="~/images/team1.jpg" alt="Jane Doe" class="img-circle" />
            <h3>Jane Doe</h3>
            <p>Owner & Pet Specialist</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 team-member">
            <img src="~/images/team2.jpg" alt="John Smith" class="img-circle" />
            <h3>John Smith</h3>
            <p>Veterinarian</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 team-member">
            <img src="~/images/team3.jpg" alt="Emily Johnson" class="img-circle" />
            <h3>Emily Johnson</h3>
            <p>Grooming Expert</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .about-us-container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    h1, h2 {
        color: #333;
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    p {
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #666;
    }
    
    .team {
        margin-top: 20px;
    }
    
    .team-member {
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    .team-member img {
        border-radius: 50%;
        width: 150px;
        height: 150px;
        object-fit: cover;
    }
    
    .team-member h3 {
        margin-top: 10px;
        color: #333;
    }
    
    .team-member p {
        color: #999;
    }
</style>
